$EXIT.text:
MACRO
&NAME    $EXIT  &REGS=(YES,NUM),   EQUATES AVAILABLE R0-RF EQU 0-15    X
               &SAVE=SAVE,        SAVE REGISTER EQUATE (REG 13)        X
               &SIZE=,            SAVE AREA SIZE (TO BE FREE'D)        X
               &RC=0              RETURN CODE (DECIMAL), OR            X
                                  &RC=(REG), OR &RC='LABEL'
.*
.*
         LCLA  &R0
         LCLA  &R1
         LCLA  &M
         LCLA  &N
.*
         LCLC  &R12
         LCLC  &R13
         LCLC  &R14
         LCLC  &R15
         LCLC  &R
         LCLC  &RCD
         LCLC  &SAV
.*
.*
&R0      SETA  0
&R1      SETA  1
.*
&R12     SETC  '12'
&R13     SETC  '13'
&R14     SETC  '14'
&R15     SETC  '15'
&R       SETC  ''
.*
.*
.*
         AIF   (K'&NAME LE 0).NONM
.*
&NAME    DS    0H
.*
.*
.NONM    AIF   ('&REGS(1)' EQ 'NO').SRC
.*
&R       SETC  'R'
         AIF   ('&REGS(2)' EQ 'NUM').SRC
.*
&R12     SETC  'C'
&R13     SETC  'D'
&R14     SETC  'E'
&R15     SETC  'F'
.*
.*
.SRC     AIF   (T'&RC EQ 'O').SREG
         AIF   (T'&RC EQ 'F').FWRC
         AIF   (T'&RC EQ 'H').HWRC
         AIF   (T'&RC EQ 'C').M255
         AIF   (T'&RC EQ 'N').SDRC
         AIF   (T'&RC NE 'U').SREG
.*
         LR    &R.&R15,&RC(1)              LOAD RETURN CODE
         AGO   .SREG
.*
.*
.SDRC    LA    &R.&R15,&RC             SET RETURN CODE
         AGO   .SREG
.*
.*
.M255    SR    &R.&R15,&R.&R15              LOAD RETURN
         IC    &R.&R15,&RC                CODE (MODULO 255)
         AGO   .SREG
.*
.*
.HWRC    LH    &R.&R15,&RC             LOAD RETURN CODE
         AGO   .SREG
.*
.*
.FWRC    L     &R.&R15,&RC             LOAD RETURN CODE
.SREG    ANOP
&SAV     SETC  '&R.&R13'
         AIF   (K'&SAVE EQ 0).NSAV
.*
&SAV     SETC  '&SAVE'
.*
.*
.NSAV    AIF   (K'&SIZE EQ 0).NSIZ
.*
         LR    &R.&R0,&SAV        TEMP SAVE POINTER
.*
.*
.NSIZ    L     &SAV,4(,&SAV)      RESTORE OLD SAVE POINTER
         AIF   (K'&SIZE EQ 0).RS14
.*
         ST    &R.&R1,24(,&SAV)         PRESERVE PARM POINTER
         LR    &R.&R1,&R.&R0            ADDR FOR FREEMAIN
         L     &R.&R0,&SIZE            SIZE OF FREEMAIN
         LA    &R.&R1,0(,&R.&R1)               FREE THE
         SVC   10                      SAVE AREA
.*
.*
.RS14    L     &R.&R14,12(,&SAV)       RESTORE RETURN ADDRESS
.*
.*
.DONE    LM    &R.&R0,&R.&R12,20(&SAV)       RESTORE REGISTERS
         BR    &R.&R14                 RETURN
         SPACE 3
         MEND

         AIF   (K'&TITLE LE 0).NTITL
.*
&TITLE(1) TITLE &TITLE(2)
.*
.NTITL   ANOP
&K       SETA  K'&STRING
         AIF   (&K GT 48).DONE
.*
&M       SETA  1
         AIF   (&K GT 0).COPY2
&K       SETA  K'&NAME
.*
.COPY1   ANOP
&STR(&M) SETC  '&NAME'(&M,1)
&M       SETA  &M+1
         AIF   (&M LE &K).COPY1
         AGO   .COPYD
.*
.COPY2   ANOP
&STR(&M) SETC  '&STRING'(&M,1)
&M       SETA  &M+1
         AIF   (&M LE &K).COPY2
.*
.COPYD   ANOP
&J       SETA  0
&M       SETA  0
.*
.EDIT    AIF   (&M EQ &K).AGIN
&M       SETA  &M+1
&I       SETA  &M
         AIF   ('&STR(&M)' NE '''').EDIT
.*
         AIF   (&J GT 0).QTCK
.*
&J       SETA  1
         AGO   .COMP
.*
.QTCK    AIF   ('&STR(&M+1)' NE '''').COMP
.*
&STR(&M) SETC  '"'
&J       SETA  0
&M       SETA  &M+1
&I       SETA  &M
.*
.COMP    ANOP
&STR(&I) SETC  '&STR(&I+1)'
&I       SETA  &I+1
         AIF   (&I LT &K).COMP
.*
&STR(&K) SETC  ' '
&K       SETA  &K-1
&M       SETA  &M-1
         AGO   .EDIT
.*
.AGIN    ANOP
&I       SETA  1
&L       SETA  &K-&N
         AIF   (&L LE 0).HEXS
.*
         AIF   (&L LE 6).CK4
.*
&L       SETA  6
.*
.CK4     AIF   (&L GT 4).SETL
.*
&J       SETA  8
         AIF   (&L GT 2).FILT
.*
&J       SETA  16
.*
.FILT    AIF   (&I GT &J).SETL
.*
&FLD(&I) SETC  '&C(2)'
&I       SETA  &I+1
         AGO   .FILT
.*
.SETL    ANOP
&L       SETA  &L+&N
.*
.LOOP    AIF   (&N EQ &L).FINI
.*
&N       SETA  &N+1
&J       SETA  1
&JL      SETA  9
.*
.MTCH    AIF   ('&STR(&N)' EQ '&C(&J)').GO
.*
&J       SETA  &J+9
&JL      SETA  &J+8
         AIF   (&J LT 424).MTCH
.*
.GO      AIF   (&J EQ &JL).LOOP
.*
&J       SETA  &J+1
&FLD(&I) SETC  '&C(&J)'
&I       SETA  &I+1
         AGO   .GO
.*
.FINI    AIF   (&I GT 48).DOIT
.*
&FLD(&I) SETC  ' '
&I       SETA  &I+1
         AGO   .FINI
.*
.DOIT    ANOP
         SPACE 2
 MNOTE *,'            &FLD(1)&FLD(9)&FLD(17)&FLD(25)&FLD(33)&FLD(41)'
 MNOTE *,'            &FLD(2)&FLD(10)&FLD(18)&FLD(26)&FLD(34)&FLD(42)'
 MNOTE *,'            &FLD(3)&FLD(11)&FLD(19)&FLD(27)&FLD(35)&FLD(43)'
 MNOTE *,'            &FLD(4)&FLD(12)&FLD(20)&FLD(28)&FLD(36)&FLD(44)'
 MNOTE *,'            &FLD(5)&FLD(13)&FLD(21)&FLD(29)&FLD(37)&FLD(45)'
 MNOTE *,'            &FLD(6)&FLD(14)&FLD(22)&FLD(30)&FLD(38)&FLD(46)'
 MNOTE *,'            &FLD(7)&FLD(15)&FLD(23)&FLD(31)&FLD(39)&FLD(47)'
 MNOTE *,'            &FLD(8)&FLD(16)&FLD(24)&FLD(32)&FLD(40)&FLD(48)'
         AGO   .AGIN
.*
.HEXS    ANOP
&HX      SETA  2*((K'&NAME)/2)+1
&BR      SETA  &HX+5
&R0      SETA  0
&R1      SETA  1
&R       SETC  ''
&R12     SETC  '12'
&R13     SETC  '13'
&R14     SETC  '14'
&R15     SETC  '15'
         AIF   (K'&TYPE EQ 0).DONE
         AIF   ('&TYPE' NE 'START').CSEC
.*
         SPACE 3
&NAME    START &ORG
         AGO   .REGS
.*
.CSEC    AIF   ('&TYPE' NE 'CSECT').DONE
.*
         SPACE 3
&NAME    CSECT
.*
.REGS    AIF   ('&REGS(1)' NE 'YES').BASE
.*
         SPACE 3
.*
R0       EQU   0                  R
R1       EQU   1                   E
R2       EQU   2                    G
R3       EQU   3                     I
R4       EQU   4                      S
R5       EQU   5                       T
R6       EQU   6                        E
R7       EQU   7                         R
R8       EQU   8
&R       SETC  'R'
         AIF   ('&REGS(2)' EQ 'NUM').NREG
.*
R9       EQU   9                  E
RA       EQU   10                  Q
RB       EQU   11                   U
RC       EQU   12                    A
RD       EQU   13                     T
RE       EQU   14                      E
RF       EQU   15                       S
&R12     SETC  'C'
&R13     SETC  'D'
&R14     SETC  'E'
&R15     SETC  'F'
         AIF   ('&REGS(2)' EQ 'HEX').BASE
.*
.NREG    ANOP
R9       EQU   9                  E
R10      EQU   10                  Q
R11      EQU   11                   U
R12      EQU   12                    A
R13      EQU   13                     T
R14      EQU   14                      E
R15      EQU   15                       S
.*
.BASE    ANOP
&SAV     SETC  '&R.&R13'
         AIF   (K'&BASE EQ 0).SAVE
         AIF   (&BASE LE 0).SAVE
.*
         SPACE 1
BASE     EQU   &BASE                 BASE REGISTER
.*
.SAVE    AIF   (K'&SAVE EQ 0).AREG
         AIF   (&SAVE LE 0).AREG
.*
         SPACE 1
SAVE     EQU   &SAVE                 SAVE REGISTER
&SAV     SETC  'SAVE'
.*
.AREG    ANOP
&K       SETA  N'&ADREG
         AIF   (&K LE 0).NTER
.*
         SPACE 1
*                                 MISCELANEOUS EQUATES
.*
.LA      AIF   (&K LE 0).NTER
.*
&N       SETA  K'&ADREG(&K)
&M       SETA  &N
.*
.LB      AIF   (&N LE 0).DA
         AIF   ('&ADREG(&K)'(&N,1) EQ '=').SB
.*
&N       SETA  &N-1
         AGO   .LB
.*
.SB      ANOP
&ADR     SETC  '&ADREG(&K)'(1,&N-1)
&ADE     SETC  '&ADREG(&K)'(&N+1,&M-&N)
&ADR     EQU   &ADE
.*
.DA      ANOP
&K       SETA  &K-1
         AGO   .LA
.*
.NTER    ANOP
         EJECT
         B     &BR.(,&R.&R15)           ENTRY POINT
         DC    X'&HX'              I.D. CHAR COUNT
         DC    CL&HX'&NAME'       MODULE I.D.
         STM   &R.&R14,&R.&R12,12(&SAV)       SAVE REGISTERS
         AIF   (&BASE LE 0).DONE
.*
         SPACE 1
         BALR  BASE,0             ESTABLISH
         USING *,BASE                  ADDRESSABILITY
         AIF   (K'&SIZE EQ 0).NSIZ
         SPACE 1
         L     &R.&R0,&SIZE            GET
         BAL   &R.&R1,*+4                SAVE
         SVC   10                      AREA
         XC    0(72,&R.&R1),0(&R.&R1)
         ST    &SAV,4(,&R.&R1)           BACK CHAIN SAVE AREAS
         ST    &R.&R1,8(,&SAV)           FORWARD CHAIN SAVE AREAS
         AGO   .SAVR
.*
.NSIZ    AIF   (K'&SECT EQ 0).RPAR
         SPACE 1
         ST    &SAV,&SECT.+4        BACK CHAIN SAVE AREAS
         LA    &R.&R1,&SECT            FORWARD CHAIN
         ST    &R.&R1,8(,&SAV)                SAVE AREAS
.*
.SAVR    LR    &SAV,&R.&R1             POINTER TO SAVE AREA
         AIF   (K'&SECT EQ 0).RPAR
.*
         USING &SECT,&SAV         ESTAB SAVE AREA ADDRESSABILITY
.*
.RPAR    AIF   ('&PARM' EQ 'NO').DONE
.*
         SPACE 1
         L     &R.&R1,4(,&SAV)        RESTORE
         LM    &R.&R0,&R.&R1,20(&R.&R1)    PARM PTR
.*
.DONE    ANOP
         SPACE 3
         MEND
